The purpose of the project entitled as “HOSPITAL MANAGEMENT SYSTEM” is to computerize the Front Office Management of Hospital to 
develop software which is user friendly simple, fast, and cost effective. It deals with the collection of patient’s information,
diagnosis details, etc. Traditionally, it was done manually. The main function of the system is register and store patient details
and doctor details and retrieve these details as and when required, and also to manipulate these details meaningfully System input 
contains patient details, diagnosis details, while system output is to get these details on to the screen. The Hospital Management 
System can be entered using a username and password. It is accessible either by an administrator or receptionist. Only they can add 
data into the database. The data can be retrieved easily. The data are well protected for personal use and makes the data processing 
very fast.
